OL,4,BMario Balotelli: Brescia defend owner
OL,5,BMassimo Cellino over comments
OL,6, Serie A side Brescia have said chairman
OL,7, Massimo Cellino's comments regarding
OL,8, striker Mario Balotelli are "a joke
OL,9, said as a paradox" that was "clearly
OL,10, misunderstood".
OL,12,FAsked why Balotelli had been dropped,
OL,13,Fex-Leeds United owner Cellino said:
OL,14,F"What can I say? That he's black and
OL,15,Fhe's working to whiten himself but he
OL,16,Fhas great difficulties in this."
OL,18,FItalian Balotelli was racially abused
OL,19,Fby Verona supporters on 3 November. He
OL,20,Fwas persuaded to remain on the pitch
OL,21,Fafter threatening to walk off.
